---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Tax Number (AFM) Greece | Taxomade">
  <!-- Hero Section with Grid Background -->
  <div class="relative pt-40 pb-32 overflow-hidden bg-slate-50">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:24px_24px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/50 via-white/80 to-slate-50"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-8 tracking-tight">Get your Greek tax number (AFM) <br/><span class="text-blue-800">—</span> fast and remote.</h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-600 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">The AFM is your gateway to living, working and banking in Greece. We register it for you.</p>
      <a href="/#configurator" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold rounded-lg text-white bg-slate-900 hover:bg-blue-800 transition-colors duration-200 shadow-sm">
        Get your AFM
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Two-column: What it is & Requirements -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-20">
      <!-- What it is Card -->
      <section class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-800 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
          What it is
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          The AFM (Αριθμός Φορολογικού Μητρώου) is your Greek tax identification number. You need it for almost everything official in Greece: registering as a freelancer, opening a bank account, signing a rental contract, paying taxes, and applying for the 50% tax break. It's the first administrative step for anyone settling in Greece.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Requirements Card -->
      <section class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-800 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
          Requirements
        </h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg text-slate-700 list-disc list-inside">
          <li>A valid passport or ID.</li>
          <li>For EU citizens: no visa needed.</li>
          <li>For non-EU citizens: typically your residence permit / visa.</li>
          <li>A Greek address or a representative (we can act via power of attorney if you're not yet in Greece).</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- How it works -->
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-20 bg-slate-50 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center">How it works</h2>

      <div class="space-y-10">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-6">
            <span class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold shadow-md">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">What you do</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">Send us a copy of your passport/ID and basic details, and sign a power of attorney so we can act for you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-6">
            <span class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-800 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold shadow-md">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">What Taxomade does</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">Our licensed local partner registers your AFM with the Greek tax authority (AADE) on your behalf — often without you needing to appear in person. You receive your AFM ready to use.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mt-10 text-sm italic text-center">This is usually quick (a few days) and is the foundation for everything that follows.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing Package -->
    <section class="max-w-md mx-auto mb-20">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden relative">
        <div class="p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Greek Tax Number (AFM)</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 mb-6">Fast, remote registration of your Greek tax ID.</p>
          <div class="flex items-baseline mb-8">
            <span class="text-5xl font-black text-slate-900">€250</span>
            <span class="text-slate-500 ml-2">/ one-off</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start text-slate-700"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-800 mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> Remote registration via PoA</li>
            <li class="flex items-start text-slate-700"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-800 mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> Fast turnaround time</li>
            <li class="flex items-start text-slate-700"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-800 mr-3 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> Fully managed by licensed partner</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/#contact" class="block w-full py-4 px-6 bg-slate-900 hover:bg-blue-800 text-white font-bold rounded-xl transition-colors duration-200 text-center">Get AFM now</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-10 text-center">FAQ</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Do EU citizens need an AFM?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">Yes, if they live, work or do financial transactions in Greece.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Can I get it before moving?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">Yes — we can register it remotely via power of attorney.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Is the AFM the same as registering as a freelancer?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">No — the AFM comes first; freelancer registration is a separate step we also handle.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Do I need it if I stay under 6 months?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">Often not for tax purposes, but you may still need it for banking or renting.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
